{"hec66d922gaf6bg495fgaac0g7342919a80ea": ["Shh. I can't hear!", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "b5e0c75d-1685-cf5d-51f0-61c3535e36c8"], "h1cf12094g187cg4741g895cgb7b44cc12a8c": ["Shh! Listen.", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "487a8737-3ead-c268-4cd8-ccdce0dd3256"], "h653b705bgb729g4ca8ga9a3g045d92ffec8c": ["<i>Listen quietly.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "8b28f42a-f4f2-c17f-2e4b-d35b1916741d"], "h8905d099g07b8g443dg8521g5fd1e6f92743": ["You shouldn't be standing out in the water. It's dangerous.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "cf427ffe-e686-246c-13b4-1945760461f8"], "hfd43ba34g7bffg42c0ga123g8443f914f36e": ["Don't you hear it? It's so peaceful.", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "e4fa8a2b-abcc-a73e-7394-14550b856dbf"], "hf74d89bcge58cg4841gad95g2c029b81a14f": ["I don't hear anything. Come back to shore.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "88bd43a6-cc03-3b27-157a-f0b50fb38c40"], "ha44182a2g18bcg44eagb7c9gd3f6fd15803e": ["<i>Focus and try to hear what he hears.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "a864e54c-7afc-fab3-e6a9-8918a4311e0c"], "h833c7ef2g2746g4324g8896g7445e1a1a262": ["*A sweet melody beckens you. It vibrates with magic - a harpy's charm.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "d26ab175-7996-fae7-c506-594428a4b1ee"], "hcdbec37bg34d8g478bg9e65g7652c981069a": ["<i>Struggle against the music's pull.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "3c82d029-82da-2c40-3c4b-f8eebfb00e6a"], "h2103a5f2gc971g4530g913ag8013ce2e8373": ["*A sweet melody plays above the waves, beckoning you - drowning out all logical thought.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "11d69513-d82b-5e1f-aca1-d6174697dd98"], "h8e1bf73age6e2g45bag83fbg648d42c9f067": ["<i>Close your eyes and listen to the song.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "e45446ae-8a78-2dfd-adfc-36d0b0c6abfa"], "hc43b9568g5191g44c0g91a1g666859244de5": ["<i>Struggle against the music's pull.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "1545cd4f-be62-8ae2-e75a-087668b3339e"], "h86a4e006gd463g4753g9393g678871a7d6d3": ["*The suffocating yearning suddenly fades as the spell breaks. You are free.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "540bdce9-6230-2892-3d44-486d1c4f4881"], "h799d1abfgafabg4263g8364gd339dfbb4da3": ["Get back - it's a trick!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "72cb5382-2608-348b-f29d-e784208c9c55"], "h699b34dega312g4c7aga726g9e00eb3da99b": ["No, no. It's just a bit of water. I only want to listen. Just a little closer...", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "0518cd2b-030b-1e65-59ae-add3a3308beb"], "haf18bbb6g327bg4cb0g81c4ga1c860eaeda8": ["<i>Drown out the music with a few verses of 'The Maid and the Merrow'.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "4faa2183-ce0a-43db-e2d2-80a59eae4375"], "h99240a88ga1f3g4857gbc0dg7c1d10466485": ["Why are you - wait, why am I wet?", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "331840ca-d144-40d0-096f-ca74d4c05a8d"], "hb2073f6eg65a0g4c4agadcdg68d51cb6d635": ["No! He's <i>ours</i>.", "e5f24d94-a1a9-40e0-b3ee-fe0480c408d3", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "736ec2d2-1ea8-2963-268a-f1e44ef6886c"], "hee69e350g7854g47a6gb3c4g18fdfe1ebab9": ["Kill! We'll KILL you!", "e5f24d94-a1a9-40e0-b3ee-fe0480c408d3", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "6a230fef-eae2-9fcb-2e1c-bfdbc432d927"], "h6330dbd1g3f89g4e08g9e87g4e5622112ae8": ["Shhh! You're ruining it. I just want to - just a little closer...", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "f2f57219-0363-a5b1-34ff-d57a79665215"], "h780ba514g12a8g4e88g8595ge76a98b4fa7f": ["<i>Roar at the top of your lungs to overpower the voice.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "8d6f68f9-7132-db7f-2c71-a1154ec6cbb5"], "h16808f64gd429g49bcg9ad3ge8d0e9bc4296": ["Auch! My ears! Wait - why am I wet?", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "93d5825d-4e8e-a3c9-8c6a-b105ea12f54a"], "h468f6de9gb444g49bfga3b5g47c7e6163ea5": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "9cfdfd24-5e77-c8f4-6c30-4e8f2e279264"], "he5fa859fg3471g4c0ega4a6ga02d0f982dea": ["*Your chest fills with yearning. You want to get closer - you <i>need </i>to get closer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "03428ac1-4c05-e77c-eadd-9e3c374ae5e8"], "h3d58c22egf9c9g44feg9cbfge25c1a733a86": ["*Just a few more steps... and you can lose yourself in that sweet song...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "371da1a6-bef8-8036-d753-a7d2eff4f89e"], "h8bd6ba9fg3cc1g44c2g91a9ge3968e8f33bb": ["<i>Pick his pockets while he's distracted.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "5a6ab054-6389-191d-a9c8-c7029deb0cf6"], "hf96a595bgdfd4g47d7g9cb1gaa28475a4454": ["*You lift the child's gold pouch as he stumbles deeper into the water, oblivious.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "ec0e1181-ef1e-6c2a-9a51-8e363f7364ca"], "h1c1a96cbg3965g4be5gb1a5g3d0919f893b5": ["What a hero.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "27ba59b5-594a-9c64-f851-2a9d8dd7c0a7"], "h27f997cbg8129g483cga0f2gddac68478b77": ["Yes, everything's gonna be fine... once I get there...", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "34ac7898-89ee-55eb-6268-2ad39f035b97"], "h856d3dbeg93ccg4103ga5f2g1db01bdedd87": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "38c0c9af-53c3-631d-54fc-8b51de4fa0aa"], "h5f0b8d83gfef5g4eeeg81e1g0a699adf59b5": ["|Karlach node: You asshat!|", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "c40ae58f-45d6-4eb2-3000-feab6532f86e"], "haa6f3f68gfcd9g499eg97b8g50051a5c8040": ["You villain! I didn't know you had it in you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "6db84313-a525-eb60-02fd-593dcfeb8880"], "h1a771cd2g303fg4c2bgaf63gbae6e21a2aa0": ["Nicely done. I hope you're intending to share.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "e5b8b03d-2778-da83-e044-85db369f85ba"], "hbbda82e8g84bfg499fga489gf0d96c1cef99": ["*You slip your hand into his pocket but find nothing.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "0f30cf87-461d-45e3-83cb-288c939fa091"], "hfef46752ga52bg42a3g985fgfced96030d44": ["Don't touch me! You won't stop me! Just a little closer...", "3b92c689-6024-4446-a6c9-584e9e8d77ca", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "a35c8fb4-4c44-2cea-c41c-c24d797c412d"], "hbe005e36g1681g45b6gb8c2g01fb27624357": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_HarpyMeal_CharmedVictim.html", "56104da2-dc47-9d65-9aa5-31d16b3c084c"]}